  "prompt": "How do I know if a shy guy likes me?",
  "response": "It can be challenging to tell if a shy guy likes you, especially because he may not express his feelings openly. However, there are subtle signs you can look for that might indicate he has feelings for you:\n\n### 1. **He Finds Reasons to Be Near You**\n   - Even if he doesn\u2019t initiate conversation, he might position himself close to you or linger around your space.\n   - He might join group activities or events where you\u2019re present.\n\n### 2. **He Acts Nervous or Awkward Around You**\n   - Shy guys often feel self-conscious around someone they like. He might stumble over his words, blush, fidget, or avoid eye contact when he\u2019s near you.\n\n### 3. **He Observes or Stares When You\u2019re Not Looking**\n   - You might catch him glancing at you when he thinks you\u2019re not paying attention.\n   - He might quickly look away when you notice.\n\n### 4. **He Makes an Effort to Talk to You**\n   - Even if he\u2019s shy, he might try to strike up conversations with you, even if they\u2019re brief or seem awkward.\n   - He might ask about your interests or remember small details you\u2019ve shared.\n\n### 5. **He Opens Up to You Slowly**\n   - If he feels comfortable around you, he might start sharing more about himself than he does with others.\n   - He might reveal personal thoughts or feelings over time.\n\n### 6. **He Tries to Help or Impress You**\n   - He might offer to help you with tasks or go out of his way to do something kind for you.\n   - He might subtly try to show off his skills or interests to get your attention.\n\n### 7. **He Reacts Positively to Your Attention**\n   - If you talk to him or compliment him, he might seem flustered but genuinely happy.\n   - He might smile more or seem more at ease when you\u2019re around.\n\n### 8. **He Gets Jealous or Protective**\n   - If he notices you talking to other guys, he might seem uncomfortable or act differently.\n   - He might try to subtly insert himself into the situation to get your attention back.\n\n### 9. **He Finds Ways to Stay Connected**\n   - He might follow you on social media, like or comment on your posts, or send you messages.\n   - He might ask for your number or find excuses to keep in touch.\n\n### 10. **His Friends Act Differently Around You**\n   - Sometimes his friends might tease him when you\u2019re around or give you knowing looks.\n   - They might mention him more often or hint that he likes you.\n\n### What You Can Do:\nIf you suspect a shy guy likes you, you can take the initiative to make him feel more comfortable:\n   - Initiate conversations and show genuine interest in him.\n   - Compliment him to boost his confidence.\n   - Spend time together in low-pressure settings to help him open up.\n   - Be patient and give him time to express his feelings.\n\nRemember, shy individuals often need more time and encouragement to feel comfortable sharing their emotions, so being kind and understanding can go a long way.",
  "temperature": 1.0,
